OneLineDescription: Auto adds highheels sound to valid boots
LongDescription:
Adds high heels sound to all found and valid boots.
Mod can be downloaded here:
Skyrim LE/SE: https://www.loverslab.com/files/file/1795-heels-sound/
Skyrim SE: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/62502


Currently adds sounds for all boots using 'HDT HighHeels System' mod: https://www.google.com/search?q=HDT+HighHeels+System and for boots with NIOHH mod data, NIOHH link: https://www.google.com/search?q=NiOverride+High+Heels+-+NIOVHH
